Celebrate the best of childhood with Cartoon Network’s Clarence, the story of an optimistic, spirited, lovable boy in the 4th grade who sees the best in all things and wants to try everything—because everything is amazing! Collects issues #1-4, and features short stories by Derek Fridolfs (Batman: Li'l Gotham) and JJ Harrison (Adventure Time)!
